Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·比利斯嗎 真是個好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有殺的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時離開 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交給你了 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥開始後已經過了5個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去聽聽其他觀察者們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作可能也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年人真讓人討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七MS小隊即將到達極限運作時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓第十六MS小隊接班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快輪到你出場了哦 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊準備出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要持續到什麼時候 這些攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少得讓人吃頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能交出Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flag隊 任務時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 格拉漢姆·艾卡 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知各機 我們的目標是那個大塊頭Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊中止的同時 我們開始俘獲作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被敵人的光束擊中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 戰鬥開始後已經15個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 你的動作很遲鈍嘛 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了本大爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 已俘獲帶翼機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意點 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還會像以前那樣突然啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官 已視線確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flags
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E陣形開始任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 約書亞他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約書亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別打亂陣形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真當你是隊長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中變形?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為你又能獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊 …什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約書亞他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣形變更為C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指尖的感覺已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想抱緊你啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是 睡美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister他們有聯繫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的Meister們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三點鐘方向 出現敵影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mobile Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Enact是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來清算上次那筆債了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊Gundam老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何啊 Agristor的等離子護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體留下 你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交部的非正式情報稱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歐大陸上進行的聯合演習中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」組織出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說雙方已經開始交火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只用四台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來挑戰近千台MS部隊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 這個世界如此扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神真主的錯嗎 還是人的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道當時…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個扭曲的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一無所成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默無聞地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUN…DAM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUN…DAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUN…DAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUN…DAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:55.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ笑顔してた　そんな僕らも　幾年も重ね過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:21:03.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う景色を　受け入れられずに　もがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:11.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:16.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:18.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:23.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:37.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:42.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:48.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れちゃいけないから Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:53.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:22:01.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この広い大地と仲間達のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:55.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經久不變的笑顏　是這樣的我們　在年輪中週而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:21:03.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦身而過的風景　卻無法剪下收藏　唯心房中絲縷焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:11.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將無謂的自尊遠遠拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:16.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用溫柔將這個世界抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:18.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:23.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告訴我你的勇氣　即使逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.31,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一個人便無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:37.78,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於我心深處　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:42.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:48.48,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為不能忘記 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:53.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:22:01.03,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這片無垠大地和同伴們的故事
